window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Welcome to Cozy Creek, a quaint tourist town nestled along the Pacific Coast. </p> <p>Daisy McDare is busy nursing a broken heart, trying to build up her interior decorator business, and baking cookies when murder strikes Cozy Creek. </p> <p>At first she leaves the investigation to Chris Crumple, the local bumbling police detective. But when Crumple arrests the wrong suspect, Daisy takes the investigation into her own hands. </p> <p>Cracking the case won't be easy. She'll need help from her pastry-baking best friend, Samantha; her wisecracking Granny Annie; and her trusty West Highland Terrier, Shamus. </p> <p>It's up to Daisy McDare to find the murderer in Cozy Creek before they strike again. </p>"; 
